<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Introduction - Data Privacy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
 </head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('partials/navbar', {currentPage: 'introduction'}); %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <h2>Introduction to Data Privacy</h2>

    <div class="key-points">
      <ul>
        <li>In the 21st century, data privacy stands as a critical pillar of digital trust, decisively shaping how personal information is collected, processed, and secured (Kuye, 2023).</li>
        <li>With the explosive growth of data-driven technologies—ranging from social media to artificial intelligence—individuals and organizations are confronted with significant challenges in safeguarding sensitive data (Liu, 2018).</li>
        <li>According to Torre, Alferez, Soltana, Sabetzadeh, & Briand (2020), global regulatory frameworks like the GDPR and New Zealand's Privacy Act 2020 aim to harmonize innovation with ethical data practices.</li>
        <li>This project investigates the technical, legal, and strategic dimensions of data privacy to provide actionable solutions for stakeholders.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #121213;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #002287;
      padding: 1.0rem 1rem;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    nav {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: #ecf0f1;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      background-color: #418dda;
    }

    main {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    main h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: #3e7ab7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    main p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    main ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      color: #34495e;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    main ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 0rem;
      background-color: #010d92;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0rem 0;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0px;
    }

    /* Active link styling */
    nav ul li a.active {
      background-color: #418dda;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
  </style>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Data Privacy. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
